<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Feb1938"><font color="red">16 February 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Also ask Lord C&apos;s sec to send the 2 copies direct here &hellip; Another thing I want is 3 copies of Paris-Soir, dimanche 13 &hellip; When you write F and F, asking them for the triangle piece you may say that before I left for Switzerland a fortnight ago I asked you when next writing to acknowledge receipt of Geoffrey F&apos;s letter to which I will reply shortly &hellip; Have you the corrections I put into the Zoo piece? Am working on slowly at my aubade which ends the book &hellip; My address is Villa Tuppenycap, Room 606, Burholzli, Bedlamshire West. Telegram. Cuckoo. </div>
